                  {
                    "cta": "Next!",
                    "text": "Hey! Today we'll learn how to open a presentation.\nA strong opening helps your audience pay attention from the start.",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/aecf754c-a5ce-44c9-829c-35b5b5daac25-Structured-Presentations---1.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Got it!",
                    "text": "First, introduce yourself and your topic.\nUse: \"Hi, I'm [name] from [team]. Today I'll talk about [topic].\"\nExample: \"Hi, I'm Ananya from the product team. Today I'll talk about our new onboarding flow.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/aecf754c-a5ce-44c9-829c-35b5b5daac25-Structured-Presentations---1.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Nice!",
                    "text": "Next, grab attention with a question.\nUse: \"Let me start with a question. [question]?\"\nExample: \"Let me start with a question. Have you ever left a sign-up page because it was too long?\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/aecf754c-a5ce-44c9-829c-35b5b5daac25-Structured-Presentations---1.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Makes sense!",
                    "text": "Finally, tell the audience what they will learn.\nUse: \"By the end, you'll know [takeaway].\"\nExample: \"By the end, you'll know our plan to reduce churn by 25%.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/aecf754c-a5ce-44c9-829c-35b5b5daac25-Structured-Presentations---1.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Start Practice!",
                    "text": "Now let's practice opening a presentation!",
                    "media": {
